## Limitations
The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all possible strategies for attracting software engineers. Additionally, the rapidly evolving nature of the tech industry means that strategies may need to be frequently updated to remain effective. The report also relies on secondary data, which may not capture the full complexity of individual organizational contexts.